          </div>
          
          <a class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold transition bg-primary-900 dark:bg-primary-100 hover:bg-primary-800 dark:hover:bg-white border-transparent text-white dark:text-primary-950 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl active:scale-95 hover:scale-105" href="https://github.com/shuo-us/shuo/releases/latest">
            开始试用
