                  </svg>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-4 text-sm dark:text-primary-200/70 text-primary-950/70">个人记忆与偏好学习</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center text-sm text-primary-950/40 dark:text-primary-200/40">—</td>
                <td class="p-4 text-center">
